_header: Death is strong and mastereth all thing
_description: The qualities of death — five couplets

BodRawC301.First Lines:
deeth is strong & mastryth al þynghe ne sparyth emperour
                    ne kyng…
BodRawC301.Last Lines:
…of werdely offys be þou notth boldded ne sparyth
                    neyþyr ȝowng ne hold

BLHar2316.First Lines: Ded is strong and maystret alle thingDed fordoth barown and king…
BLHar2316.Last Lines: …Man of ȝi lyf be nowht to boldffor ded ne sparet ying ne old
